---
title: One-Pan Hearty Pork Chili with Jack’s Kidney Beans
description: It doesn’t matter if the weather’s hot or cold where you are—it’s chili season! In this version, we’re keeping things simmering with ground pork, kidney beans, poblano peppers, and our special Mexican spice blend, which has just the tiniest bit of heat. It’s mild enough for your kids to gobble up, but with plenty of flavor to satisfy the adults—just break out the hot sauce if you like it scorching!
